<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Plot Purchase Confirmation - PlotVille</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #0369a1 100%);
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        
        .tagline {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            color: #e0f2fe;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .title {
            color: #1e3a8a;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .message {
            color: #4b5563;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0891b2 0%, #06b6d4 100%);
            color: white !important;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.3);
        }
        
        .button:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #06b6d4 0%, #0891b2 100%);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.4);
        }
        
        .details-box {
            background: #f0f9ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #0891b2;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .detail-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0f2fe;
        }
        
        .detail-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e3a8a;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #4b5563;
        }
        
        .highlight {
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #7dd3fc 0%, #7dd3fc 100%);
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: 100% 0.3em;
            background-position: 0 88%;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0 2px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: #1e3a8a;
            color: #e0f2fe;
            padding: 25px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .footer-links {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        
        .footer-link {
            color: #7dd3fc;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
        
        .footer-link:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .copyright {
            margin-top: 15px;
            opacity: 0.8;
            color: #bae6fd;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .button {
                display: block;
                margin: 25px auto;
            }
            
            .detail-item {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">PlotVille</div>
            <div class="tagline">Your Gateway to Premium Real Estate</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h1 class="title">ðŸŽ‰ Plot Purchase Confirmed!</h1>
            
            <p class="message">
                Congratulations <span class="highlight"><%= username %></span>! Your purchase has been successfully processed.
            </p>
            
            <div class="details-box">
                <h3 style="color: #1e3a8a; margin-bottom: 15px;">Purchase Details:</h3>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Plot Reference:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= plot.reference %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Location:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= plot.location %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Size:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= plot.size %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Purchase Amount:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= plot.amount %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Transaction ID:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= transactionId %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Purchase Date:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= purchaseDate %></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p class="message">
                Your plot documents and ownership certificate will be processed and available in your dashboard within 3-5 business days.
            </p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= frontendUrl %>/dashboard/plots" class="button">View My Plots</a>
            </div>
            
            <p class="message">
                Thank you for investing with PlotVille. We're excited to be part of your real estate journey!
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="<%= frontendUrl %>" class="footer-link">Visit Website</a>
                <a href="<%= frontendUrl %>/contact" class="footer-link">Contact Support</a>
                <a href="<%= frontendUrl %>/privacy" class="footer-link">Privacy Policy</a>
            </div>
            <div class="copyright">
                &copy; <%= currentYear %> PlotVille. All rights reserved.<br>
                <small>This email was sent to <%= email %></small>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>